LocalizedLabels.Label: Person with whom a business unit has a relationship, such as customer, supplier, and colleague.
Select the contact's role within the company or sales process, such as decision maker, employee, or influencer.
Type additional information to describe the contact, such as an excerpt from the company's website.
Type the contact's first name to make sure the contact is addressed correctly in sales calls, email, and marketing campaigns.
Type the contact's last name to make sure the contact is addressed correctly in sales calls, email, and marketing campaigns.

EntityDefinitions.MobileOfflineFilters:
<fetch version="1.0" output-format="xml-platform" mapping="logical" distinct="false">
			<entity name="contact">
				<filter type="and">
					<condition attribute="modifiedon" operator="last-x-days" value="10"/>
				</filter>
			</entity>
		</fetch>
